msgstr "正在检查服务…"

msgid "Choose a cooling profile or set a manual output. Safety limits remain active in every mode."
msgstr "选择散热方案或设置手动输出。所有模式都会保留安全限制。"

msgid "Comma-separated temperature:percent points. The controller interpolates between points."
msgstr "使用逗号分隔“温度:百分比”控制点，控制器会在各点之间插值。"

