msgstr "来自本地模块缓存"

msgid "H5000M Cooling"
msgstr "H5000M 散热管理"

msgid "Hottest available sensor"
msgstr "可用传感器中的最高温度"

msgid "Kernel protection only"
msgstr "仅内核保护"

msgid "Kernel safety floor"
msgstr "内核安全下限"

msgid "Kernel thermal protection is always retained. Requested output may be raised automatically when the kernel requires more cooling."
msgstr "内核温控保护始终保留；当内核需要更多散热时，实际输出会自动高于请求值。"

msgid "Live fan policy, temperature sensors and kernel safety protection."
msgstr "实时查看风扇策略、温度传感器和内核安全保护。"

msgid "Loading…"
msgstr "正在载入…"

msgid "Manual PWM output"
msgstr "手动 PWM 输出"

msgid "No tachometer signal is exposed by the hardware/driver"
msgstr "硬件或驱动没有提供转速脉冲信号"

msgid "No valid sensor"
msgstr "没有有效传感器"

msgid "Not supported"
msgstr "不支持"

msgid "Operating mode"
msgstr "运行模式"

msgid "Performance"
msgstr "性能"

msgid "Policy"
msgstr "策略"

msgid "Policy reason"
msgstr "策略原因"

msgid "Prevents repeated speed changes around a curve point."
msgstr "避免温度在曲线控制点附近波动时反复改变转速。"

msgid "Quiet"
msgstr "静音"

msgid "Requested output"
msgstr "请求输出"

msgid "Response & safety"
msgstr "响应与安全"

msgid "Seconds between control decisions. The dashboard refreshes independently."
msgstr "两次控制决策之间的秒数；仪表盘使用独立的刷新周期。"

msgid "Speed-down delay"
msgstr "降速延迟"

msgid "Startup boost PWM"
msgstr "启动助推 PWM"

msgid "Startup boost duration"
msgstr "启动助推时长"

msgid "Temperature hysteresis"
msgstr "温度滞回"

msgid "Temperatures must increase from 0–150 °C and percentages must be 0–100."
msgstr "温度必须在 0–150 °C 范围内递增，百分比必须在 0–100 范围内。"

msgid "The hottest-sensor option considers CPU, Ethernet PHY, Wi-Fi and the available 5G modem cache."
msgstr "最高温度模式会综合 CPU、以太网 PHY、Wi-Fi 和可用的 5G 模块缓存温度。"

msgid "The kernel safety floor may raise the effective output above this value."
msgstr "内核安全下限可能使实际输出高于此设置值。"

msgid "Unavailable"
msgstr "不可用"

msgid "Use comma-separated temperature:percent points, for example 35:0,45:50,70:80,90:100."
msgstr "请使用逗号分隔“温度:百分比”控制点，例如 35:0,45:50,70:80,90:100。"

msgid "Wait this many seconds before lowering fan output; temperature increases are applied immediately."
msgstr "降低风扇输出前等待指定秒数；温度升高会立即响应。"

msgid "When disabled, the fan follows the kernel thermal protection level only."
msgstr "关闭后，风扇将仅跟随内核温控保护等级。"

msgid "Wi-Fi radios"
msgstr "Wi-Fi 射频"

msgid "%s · kernel safety floor"
msgstr "%s · 内核安全下限"

msgid "Waiting before speed down"
msgstr "等待降速"

msgid "Automatic curve"
msgstr "自动曲线"

msgid "Manual request"
msgstr "手动请求"

msgid "Kernel protection"
msgstr "内核保护"

msgid "Sensor failsafe"
msgstr "传感器故障保护"

msgid "Curve failsafe"
msgstr "曲线故障保护"
